{"tid":1550552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩係慈雲山大嗌光復香港既巴打","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:19.000Z","uid":140590,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"079528859203305f2b63152643843ea3f721b498","tid":1550552,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢個藍絲社區想岀聲真係好撚麻煩好撚多阻濟<br />\n你好勇敢！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"0b21fbb2cb00a465bc81bb8532e455f5997fb2d8","tid":1550552,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"469487e2710110e9326686239cf70abe9c8f99e6","tid":1550552,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"a736046af3d8196a3a394aa58715ea19c0cc4bc2","tid":1550552,"uid":101625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa67c470f50736d02ff864d57412d46506d5af39","tid":1550552,"ui